exercises.title: Jumping Jacks
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet together, jump while spreading arms and legs, then return to start position. Repeat.

exercises.title: High Knees
exercises.instructions: Run in place while lifting your knees as high as possible, engaging your core.

exercises.title: Butt Kicks
exercises.instructions: Run in place while kicking your heels toward your glutes.

exercises.title: Mountain Climbers
exercises.instructions: Start in a high plank and bring knees towards your chest alternately at a fast pace.

exercises.title: Burpees
exercises.instructions: Squat down, jump back into a plank, do a push-up, return to squat, and jump up.

exercises.title: Skater Jumps
exercises.instructions: Jump side to side in a skating motion, keeping your back foot off the ground.

exercises.title: Fast Feet
exercises.instructions: Run in place quickly with small, rapid steps.

exercises.title: Lateral Shuffles
exercises.instructions: Bend your knees slightly and shuffle side to side quickly.

exercises.title: Spot Jogging
exercises.instructions: Jog in place with a steady rhythm.

exercises.title: Running Man
exercises.instructions: Move arms and legs as if sprinting but remain in place.

exercises.title: Cross Jacks
exercises.instructions: Perform jumping jacks while crossing arms and legs alternately.

exercises.title: Star Jumps
exercises.instructions: Jump explosively from a squat position, extending arms and legs outward.

exercises.title: Speed Skaters
exercises.instructions: Jump laterally from one foot to another in a skating motion.

exercises.title: Boxer Shuffle
exercises.instructions: Shuffle weight from one foot to the other in a light, bouncing motion.

exercises.title: Split Jumps
exercises.instructions: Jump into a lunge position and switch legs mid-air before landing.

exercises.title: Plank
exercises.instructions: Lie face down, place forearms on the ground, push up onto toes and forearms, keep back straight, hold position.

exercises.title: Side Plank
exercises.instructions: Lie on one side, prop yourself up on one forearm, stack feet, keep body straight, hold position.

exercises.title: Bicycle Crunches
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, hands behind head, bring opposite elbow to opposite knee in a pedaling motion.

exercises.title: Russian Twists
exercises.instructions: Sit with knees bent, lean back slightly, twist torso side to side while holding hands together.

exercises.title: Reverse Crunches
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, lift legs up, curl hips off the floor, slowly lower down.

exercises.title: Flutter Kicks
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, lift legs slightly off the ground, alternate kicking up and down.

exercises.title: Leg Raises
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, lift legs straight up, lower them slowly without touching the ground.

exercises.title: V-Ups
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, lift legs and upper body simultaneously, touch hands to feet, return to start.

exercises.title: Dead Bug
exercises.instructions: Lie on back, lift arms and legs, lower opposite arm and leg while keeping core engaged.

exercises.title: Seated Knee Tucks
exercises.instructions: Sit on the floor, lift feet, pull knees toward chest, extend legs outward and repeat.

exercises.title: Plank Shoulder Taps
exercises.instructions: Start in a high plank position, tap each shoulder with the opposite hand while maintaining a stable core and level hips.

exercises.title: Hollow Body Hold
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, press lower back into floor, extend arms overhead and legs straight out while lifting shoulders and legs off the ground.

exercises.title: Bird Dog
exercises.instructions: Start on hands and knees, extend opposite arm and leg simultaneously while keeping your back flat and core engaged.

exercises.title: Superman Hold
exercises.instructions: Lie on stomach, lift arms and legs simultaneously, hold position, lower down.

exercises.title: Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Start in a plank, lower body by bending elbows, push back up to start position.

exercises.title: Diamond Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Place hands in a diamond shape under chest, lower body, push back up.

exercises.title: Triceps Dips
exercises.instructions: Sit on the ground, hands behind you, lift hips, bend elbows to lower body, push back up.

exercises.title: Wide Arm Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Place hands wider than shoulder-width apart, lower chest to floor while keeping elbows out to sides, then push back up.

exercises.title: Pike Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Start in a downward dog position, lower head towards ground, push back up.

exercises.title: Super Slow Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Perform a push up as slow as possible

exercises.title: Isometric Push-Up Hold
exercises.instructions: Perform a standard push up and hold at the lowest point

exercises.title: Wall Sit
exercises.instructions: Lean against wall, lower until knees at 90 degrees, hold position.

exercises.title: Squat Hold
exercises.instructions: Perform a squat and hold at the lowest point

exercises.title: Lunge Hold
exercises.instructions: Perform a lunge and hold

exercises.title: Calf Raises
exercises.instructions: Stand still, raise up onto tiptoes, hold and lower.

exercises.title: Step Through Lunges
exercises.instructions: Go from reverse to forward lunge

exercises.title: Side Lunges
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet together, step one foot out to the side, bend that knee while keeping the other leg straight, then push back to starting position.

exercises.title: Bodyweight Squats
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width, bend knees, lower hips down, push back up.

exercises.title: Ab Crunch Twist
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, lift shoulders off the ground, and twist your torso to alternate sides while engaging your core.

exercises.title: Alternate Deadbug
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back with arms extended upward and legs raised with knees bent. Extend one leg and the opposite arm simultaneously while keeping your lower back pressed into the floor.

exercises.title: Bird Dog 2
exercises.instructions: Start on all fours, extend opposite arm and leg simultaneously while maintaining balance and core engagement, then return to starting position and repeat with other side.

exercises.title: Flow Yoga
exercises.instructions: Move through a sequence of yoga poses with fluid transitions, focusing on breath coordination and mindful movement.

exercises.title: Plank Climbers
exercises.instructions: Start in a high plank position, bring one knee toward your chest, then quickly switch legs in a climbing motion while maintaining a stable core.

exercises.title: Up Down Plank
exercises.instructions: Start in a forearm plank, push up to a high plank one arm at a time, then lower back down to forearm plank one arm at a time. Repeat the sequence with control.

exercises.title: Hindu Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Start in a downward dog position, lower your chest forward and down into a cobra position, then push back up into downward dog.

exercises.title: Archer Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Begin in a wide push-up stance, lower your chest toward one arm while keeping the other extended, then push back up and switch sides.

exercises.title: Step-Back Lunges
exercises.instructions: Step one foot backward into a deep lunge, keeping the front knee at 90 degrees, then push back up to the starting position and repeat on the other leg.

exercises.title: Cossack Squats
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet wide apart, lower your body to one side while keeping the opposite leg extended, then push back up and switch sides.

exercises.title: Broad Jumps
exercises.instructions: Squat down and explode forward into a jump, landing softly with bent knees to absorb impact.

exercises.title: Bear Crawl
exercises.instructions: Start on all fours with knees slightly lifted, crawl forward by moving opposite hand and foot together.

exercises.title: Seal Jacks
exercises.instructions: Jump while opening and closing your arms and legs simultaneously, keeping arms parallel to the ground.

exercises.title: Reverse Plank
exercises.instructions: Sit on the floor, place hands behind you, lift hips up, keeping body straight from head to heels.

exercises.title: Standing Side Crunches
exercises.instructions: Stand tall, raise one knee while bringing the same-side elbow down to meet it, then return to the starting position and repeat on the other side.

exercises.title: Windshield Wipers
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, lift legs straight up, slowly rotate them side to side while keeping your core engaged.

exercises.title: Lateral Bounds
exercises.instructions: Jump sideways from one foot to another, landing softly while maintaining balance.

exercises.title: Quadruped Rocking
exercises.instructions: Start on all fours, rock back and forth to improve hip mobility and core stability.

exercises.title: Jefferson Curls
exercises.instructions: Stand tall, slowly curl your spine downward, reaching toward your toes while keeping legs straight, then return to standing.
